706991f-a.title: Brooklyn: Surf Ave. - 16th St. W.
706991f-a.text:
Surf Ave., north side, west from West 16th Street. (Coney Island).
July 1, 1936.
L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

706993f-c.title: Brooklyn: Surf Ave. - 16th St. W.
706993f-c.text:
(1)
Surf Ave., south side, between west 16th and 19th (right) Streets,
showing Geo. C. Tilyou's Steeplechase Park; Carousel and Ferris Wheel.
August 9, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, a more extensive view westward.
August 9, 1932.
L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(3)
The same, showing the stands at the swimming pool; the ferris
wheel, and the bath house. At the right is West 19th Street.
July 4, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
